data.description: This adorable 3-bedroom ranch is perfectly nestled between Union City limits and I-44. It has many upgrades including quartz countertops, updated bathrooms, a gas stove, LG appliances, and a HUGE 4 seasons room with a new dedicated heating/cooling unit. It has newer windows, doors, a metal roof, wide gutters with guards, and stunning matured landscaping. This property comes with 3.2 acres and a 2700 sq ft heated, concrete floor garage that is tall enough to park your RV with its 11 ft ceiling. Relax at the end of a hard day on the large wraparound deck at the gas fire pit where there is plenty of room for seating and tables. Cook a gourmet meal at the covered outdoor Kitchen/BBQ area. Perfect for Entertaining. This property is a must-see.
